            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">焦慮加劇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科在香港的看跌押注一度攀升至十年高位，因投資者押注在該開發商意外尋求對其債券展期後，其股價的螺旋式下跌將持續。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">超預期韌性</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經合組織稱世界經濟面對關稅表現出超預期的韌性，該機構上調對美國和歐元區今明兩年成長預期，預測英國央行明年6月底前會再降息兩次。美國財長貝森特預計，2026年經濟成長率將達到4%，第一季度將看到非常可觀的退稅額。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消費疲軟</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一項民間調查顯示，中國服務業活動擴張速度為五個月來最慢，進一步證明消費需求疲軟，給正在放緩的經濟帶來更大壓力。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-300242c4-d70e-3da9-86fe-2fc9e9b17fbe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">起訴</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣檢方指控東京威力科創未能阻止員工竊取台積電商業機密，使這場牽涉晶片產業兩家關鍵亞洲公司的爭端進一步升級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「突擊式」提升</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，OpenAI執行長Sam Altman正在重新調配內部資源，以加速改進ChatGPT，並宣布拉響「紅色警報」，這將推遲其他項目的工作。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"觀看：據The Information報導，OpenAI執行長Sam Altman拉響「紅色警報」，加速改進ChatGPT。Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LD37fxPcNgutShX.MVkjeg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0ac6177d5ed839af326b861436e02b45\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看：據The Information報導，OpenAI執行長Sam Altman拉響「紅色警報」，加速改進ChatGPT。Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-051758060.html",
